	dprr:hasNoteText "In MRR 2.442, 31 B.C., refer, on his coins, also to Crawford, RRC 1.542-543, no. 546, 31 B.C. Acclaimed imperator when serving first under Antony and then under Octavian, in the Cyrenaica. See G. Perl, Klio 52, 1970, 319-354, esp. 352-353; 53, 1971, 369-379, esp. 378.\n" ;
	dprr:hasID 7490 .
